OL,3,C'Kicking out' Tories is only the first
OL,4,Cstep of change, union chief tells
OL,5,CLabour
OL,7,FSpeaking ahead of an address to the
OL,8,FScottish Labour Party conference in
OL,9,FGlasgow on Friday, Ms Foyer said: "Any
OL,10,Fparty of Labour ` UK, Scottish or
OL,11,Fotherwise ` must be unequivocally on
OL,12,Fthe side of working people and build
OL,13,Four public services back to a level
OL,14,Fworthy of our public sector workers.
OL,16,F"Kicking the Tories out of power is
OL,17,Fthe first step. The next is ensuring
OL,18,Fany incoming Labour government
OL,19,Ffundamentally alters the balance of
OL,20,Fpower in our economy.
