OL,3,C'Kicking out' Tories is only the first
OL,4,Cstep of change, union chief tells
OL,5,CLabour
OL,7,F"Scottish Labour can help. They can
OL,8,Fback our tax proposals, hold the
OL,9,FScottish Government to account and
OL,10,Fensure we build a progressive Scotland
OL,11,Fwhere wealth is shared.
OL,13,F"It shouldn't be radical to suggest
OL,14,Fthose who earn the most should invest
OL,15,Fthe most into the public services we
OL,16,Fall rely on.
